# RAG — Claude Code CLI MCP Configuration

## Configuration File Locations (2026)

### PRIMARY: ~/.claude.json
**Location:** User's HOME directory (NOT inside ~/.claude/)
**Scope:** User-level MCP servers (applies across all projects unless overridden)
**Format:** JSON with top-level "projects" object

### SECONDARY: .mcp.json
**Location:** Project root directory
**Scope:** Project-scoped (team/version control friendly)
**Format:** JSON configuration for project-specific servers

### LOCAL: .claude/settings.local.json
**Location:** Inside project directory
**Scope:** Local project settings
**Note:** Pre-commit hook configuration, IDE settings

